```

---

## Key Features Checklist

- [ ] CSV upload with drag & drop
- [ ] Auto-detect column names
- [ ] Gemini-powered profile enrichment
- [ ] Intelligent garbage filtering using AI
- [ ] Real-time progress updates
- [ ] Auto-save every 25 profiles
- [ ] Semantic search (embeddings or TF-IDF)
- [ ] Results ranked by relevance
- [ ] Export to CSV
- [ ] Mobile responsive UI
- [ ] Error handling with fallbacks

---

## Algorithms Used

| Algorithm | Purpose | Implementation |
|-----------|---------|----------------|
| **TF-IDF** | Text vectorization | sklearn or custom |
| **Cosine Similarity** | Similarity scoring | sklearn or custom |
| **N-grams** | Multi-word phrase matching | (1,2) bigrams |
| **Gemini Embeddings** | Semantic search | Google AI API |
| **LLM Extraction** | Smart info extraction | Gemini Pro |
| **Pattern Matching** | Backup validation | Regex rules |

---

## Important Notes

1. **Rate Limiting**: Add 2-3 second delays between API calls
2. **Error Handling**: Always have fallbacks when AI fails
3. **Cost Management**: Gemini API has usage limits - cache results
4. **Privacy**: Don't store sensitive data unnecessarily
5. **Progress Saving**: Save frequently to prevent data loss

---

Build this app with clean, modular code and beautiful UI. The AI enrichment should feel magical — users upload a basic CSV and get rich, detailed professional profiles back!

